data.description: OPEN HOUSE THIS SATURDAY! This beautiful Ryland home is in the Windmill Farms community. It boast an open floor plan and lots of space. The kitchen has been updated with new counter tops and bright white backsplash. Brand new carpet in all rooms and game room. Huge covered patio is the perfect place to relax by the above ground pool. There is a swing gate on the left side of the home that can fit a trailer or boat. The garage has storage cabinets and also ceiling mounted storage that will stay. New paint throughout this home brings that new home feel. Come see this gem before it is gone. The Vivint security system will also stay with the new owners.
